msgid "Prepare the transaction"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:52
msgid ""
"So far, the node's main account is a regular account. A "
":ref:`multisigaccountmodificationtransaction` will be announced that will"
" turn it into a :doc:`../../concepts/multisig-account` with a single "
"cosignatory: the **external account**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:54
msgid ""
"This means that **any operation** on the main account will **require the "
"signature** of the external account."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:56
msgid ""
"This transaction will be prepared by the service provider using ``symbol-"
"cli`` and sent to the customer for signing."
msgstr ""

